node.text: Ahh yesterday was weird. Weather was relentless. Luckily this situation never happens but it was tough to take. Shoutout of love in particular to the fans in the stands. It was cold, wet, windy, yet still managed to see some shirtless with cold beers 😆 Thank you for being lovers of the sport and hanging through it all. Sorry mother nature wasn’t on our side to make something meaningful happen. Well, it’s a 200th race I’ll remember that’s for sure 🤷🏻‍♂️
